│   "thoughts": "### 1. Understanding the Issue\n\nThe `indvars` pass is crashing │
│ with a `SIGABRT` signal due to a failed assertion in `llvm::dyn_cast`. The      │
│ backtrace indicates that a `nullptr` is being passed to a `dyn_cast` that       │
│ expects a valid `llvm::Instruction*`. This occurs during the induction variable │
