│ return false;\n```\n\nThe edit is to add a check for `WideInc` before the       │
│ `isa<BinaryOperator>` check.\n\n**Edit Point:**\n\n*   **File**:                │
│ `llvm/lib/Transforms/Utils/ScalarEvolutionExpander.cpp`\n*   **Lines**:         │
│ 822-825\n*   **Original Code**:\n    ```cpp\n    bool                           │
│ SCEVExpander::canReuseFlagsFromOriginalIVInc(PHINode *OrigPhi,\n                │
│ PHINode *WidePhi,\n                                                             │
│ Instruction *OrigInc,\n                                                         │
