│ `indvars` pass was caused by an inadequate handling of cases where the widened  │
│ induction variable's increment instruction could not be found or was not a      │
│ simple binary operation, particularly in the presence of undefined behavior     │
│ like division by zero. The proposed fix adds a necessary null check in          │
